Package: gridpattern
Type: Package
Title: 'grid' Pattern Grobs
Version: 0.1.0-26
Authors@R: c(person("Mike", "FC", role = "aut", comment = "Patterns extracted from ggpattern"),
        person("Trevor L", "Davis", role=c("aut", "cre"), email="trevor.l.davis@gmail.com"),
        person("Thomas Lin", "Pedersen", role = "ctb", comment = "new_data_frame() copied from ggplot2"))
Description: 'grid' grobs that fill in a user-defined area with various patterns.  Includes enhanced versions of the geometric and image-based patterns originally contained in the 'ggpattern' package as well as completely new patterns plus support for custom user-defined patterns.
URL: https://trevorldavis.com/R/gridpattern/, https://github.com/trevorld/gridpattern
BugReports: https://github.com/trevorld/gridpattern/issues
